Cost-effectiveness of a blended physiotherapy intervention compared to usual 
physiotherapy in patients with hip and/or knee osteoarthritis: a cluster 
randomized controlled trial.

Kloek CJJ(1)(2)(3)(4), van Dongen JM(5), de Bakker DH(6)(7), Bossen D(8), Dekker 
J(9)(10), Veenhof C(11)(12).

Author information:
(1)Tranzo, Tilburg University, Tilburg, the Netherlands. corelien.kloek@hu.nl.
(2)Netherlands Institute for Health Services Research (NIVEL), Utrecht, the 
Netherlands. corelien.kloek@hu.nl.
(3)Department of Rehabilitation, Physiotherapy Sciences and Sports, Brain Center 
Rudolf Magnus, University Medical Center Utrecht, Utrecht, the Netherlands. 
