Physiological study of pulmonary involvement in adults with cystic fibrosis 
through simulated modeling of different clinical scenarios.

Rodríguez Sousa AA(1), Barandica Fernández JM(2), Miller J(3), Mir-Montejano 
M(4).

Author information:
(1)Biological Sciences Faculty, University Complutense of Madrid, C/ José 
Antonio Nováis 2, 28040, Madrid, Spain. antonr05@ucm.es.
(2)Biological Sciences Faculty, University Complutense of Madrid, C/ José 
Antonio Nováis 2, 28040, Madrid, Spain.
(3)National Museum of Natural Sciences-Superior Council of Scientific 
